                <h3 style="text-align: justify;">1. Scope</h3>
                <br>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">1.1 CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht has developed a Platform for the re-marketing of vehicles whereby leasing companies, car manufacturers, other companies and natural persons acting for professional purposes or not can advertise Vehicles they wish to sell, and professional and recognised car dealers can submit an Offer for the purchase of Vehicles.</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">1.2 These Terms and Conditions govern the relation between CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht and Buyer in relation to Buyer's use of the Platform and in relation to the offering, sale and delivery of all Vehicles from or on behalf of CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht to Buyer.</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">1.3 Registration for the Platform and any access or use of the Platform, including making an Offer in relation to any Vehicle, shall qualify as unconditional acceptance by Buyer of these Terms and Conditions.</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">1.4 Buyer agrees to waive its own general and special terms and conditions, even where it is stated therein that only those conditions may apply, and even if such terms and conditions were not protested by CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht.</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">1.5 These Terms and Conditions constitute the entire understanding between CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht and Buyer with respect to the subject matter hereof, and supersede all prior representations, negotiations, understandings, agreements and undertakings, whether written or oral, with respect to the subject matter hereof.</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">1.6 Buyer expressly acknowledges having read, understood and agreed with all the present terms and conditions. Specifically, Buyer is in agreement with the principles regarding Vehicle Information, warranty, conformity and complaints and liability as set out in clauses 8 to 11 of these Terms and Conditions.</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">1.7 In relation to CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht Sales, these Terms and Conditions operate as a framework governing each CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht Sale. Each CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht Sale shall be deemed to constitute a separate agreement between CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht and Buyer and each such CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht Sale shall be subject to these Terms and Conditions.</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"> <a name="2">&nbsp;</a> </p>
                <h3 style="text-align: justify;">2. Definitions</h3>
                <br>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">In these Terms and Conditions, the following terms and expressions shall have the following meanings:</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Affiliate:</strong> with respect to a Party, any other company or person that, directly or indirectly, Controls or is Controlled by or is under common Control with such company;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Auction:</strong> the process described in clause 5.1;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Auction Closing:</strong> the date and time as from which the Buyer Community can no longer submit Buyer Community Offers in relation to an Auction, as specified for each Auction on the Platform;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Auction Fees:</strong> the administrative fee payable by Buyer for each Vehicle purchased via the Platform;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Auction Rules:</strong> means the specific rules that may apply to an Auction, as specified on the Platform for each Auction. Such Auction Rules may relate to, by way of example and without limitation, the minimum amount below which no offers are admissible and/or the visibility of Buyer's Offer to the other members of the Buyer Community;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Business Day:</strong> any day that is not a Saturday, Sunday or public holiday in the country of establishment of CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Buyer:</strong> the natural person or legal entity who is registered for use of the Platform, as identified in the Registration Form;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Buyer Community:</strong> the Buyer and any other buyers registered on the Platform;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Buyer Community Offers:</strong> has the meaning given to it in clause 5.1.2;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Control:</strong> has the meaning given to it in article 5 of the Belgian Companies Code;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht:</strong> CarSloter Europe NV or its Affiliate, as specified in the Registration Form in accordance with clause 3.4;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht:</strong> CarSloter Europe NV and/or any CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht Affiliate, as applicable;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht Sale Confirmation:</strong> has the meaning given to it in clause 6.1.2;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht Vehicle Description:</strong> means the description of the Vehicle provided by CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht during the Auction;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Country Fees:</strong> the administrative and logistics fee payable by Buyer for each Vehicle purchased via the Platform, depending on the country where the Seller offers the Vehicle for sale and the country in which Buyer is established;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht:</strong> European Car Auction and Distribution Solutions NV/SA, with registered office at Radarweg 18 1042 AA Amsterdam Netherlands, with company number 0867.129.211; VAT NL851940900B01;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht Affiliate:</strong> any of the CarSloter  - Rederij Slotergracht entities as described in the company details on www.CarSloter.eu.</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>E-Invoice:</strong> &nbsp;an invoice which has been issued and sent in an electronic format as chosen by CarSloter Europe. This is the legal form of invoice sent by CarSloter Europe; </p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Export:</strong> &nbsp;a supply of goods that are delivered and carried outside of the European Union;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Export Documents:</strong> all duly and fully completed document as are legally required in relation to, and as are necessary to prove the transport of the Vehicle in case of Export;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Evidence:</strong> all documention necessary to prove something. (i.e. but not limited to: Transport Documents, Export Documents, transporteur stamped and signed documentation to prove the dispatch and/or transport of the Vehicle from one place to another);</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Intra-Community Supply:</strong> a supply of goods that are transported by or on behalf of the supplier or the person to whom the supply is made from a European Union Member State to another European Union Member State;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Losses:</strong> any damage, loss, claim, demand, damage claimed by third parties, cost, tax or expense of whatever nature;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Means of Access:</strong> user ID, password and such other access means as may be required to access and use the Platform;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Offer:</strong> the offer submitted by Buyer via the Platform in relation to the purchase by Buyer from CarSloter Europe of one of more Vehicles as detailed in clause 5.1.2;</p>
