                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Platform:</strong> the online platform operated by CarSloter Europe NV via which Buyer is able to submit Offers for the purchase of Vehicles, accessible via www.CarSloter.eu or such other URL as CarSloter Europe may inform Buyer of from time to time&nbsp;or via the mobile app, available for <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.carsontheweb&amp;hl=en">Android</a> and <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/be/app/CarSloter-com/id1306619811?mt=8">iOS</a>;&nbsp;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Purchase Price:</strong> in relation to each CarSloter Europe Sale, the Offered Price, the Auction Fees for all Vehicles, the Country Fees for all Vehicles and the Transport Fees, increased with all applicable Taxes;</p>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Registration Form:</strong>the form (to be) duly completed by Buyer during the registration process for the Platform. It includes i.a. valid VAT number, proof of business registration and copy of ID of the owner/manager of the registered company, all scan of original documents with clear links;</p>
